00:05:16.426 --> 00:05:20.317
your attention goes to other's kundalini as well.

00:05:21.729 --> 00:05:25.199
That means, till now your attention could go to three places

00:05:26.312 --> 00:05:28.818
and now it goes to fourth place

00:05:28.843 --> 00:05:31.126
which is NIRAKAR SHAKTI ( formless power).

00:05:31.151 --> 00:05:35.872
And the moment you go into that state, you go beyond your thoughts

00:05:35.897 --> 00:05:39.992
and watch you mind, intellect and body in the witness state.

00:05:42.299 --> 00:05:49.901
Now those from whose hands the cool breeze is flowing

00:05:53.634 --> 00:05:59.214
these vibrations we have got so effortlessly

00:05:59.239 --> 00:06:02.535
that we don't know what a great thing we have got!

00:06:02.560 --> 00:06:07.684
The first biggest problem is

00:06:07.709 --> 00:06:10.898
'How did we get such a great thing so easily?'

00:06:11.422 --> 00:06:13.924
For example, just understand like this

00:06:13.949 --> 00:06:19.213
that a human birth we get so easily

00:06:19.238 --> 00:06:24.026
that we don't know that to get a human birth

00:06:24.051 --> 00:06:27.067
after struggling for so many births

00:06:27.092 --> 00:06:30.034
with great difficulty we get human birth

00:06:30.725 --> 00:06:32.726
and its rebirth

00:06:33.284 --> 00:06:36.344
after a great struggle for all the births we had

00:06:36.403 --> 00:06:38.703
and after a lot of seeking, one can get rebirth.

00:06:39.347 --> 00:06:41.925
But this is happening so easily

00:06:41.950 --> 00:06:45.490
that we are not able to understand its value.

00:06:46.191 --> 00:06:50.048
We also think that how did it happen so quickly.

00:06:52.155 --> 00:06:56.633
The reason was that until now you were seeking everything outside

00:06:56.658 --> 00:06:59.021
and it is within you.

00:06:59.109 --> 00:07:01.730
For example, there is a diamond within you

00:07:01.755 --> 00:07:04.064
and you are searching for it all over the world

00:07:04.089 --> 00:07:05.948
and it was found lying within you only.

00:07:06.000 --> 00:07:08.647
Then someone tells you that the diamond is here only

00:07:08.672 --> 00:07:10.151
and tells you even the route.

00:07:10.176 --> 00:07:11.296
You pick up the diamond.

00:07:11.321 --> 00:07:14.642
Will you say,"How did i get it in no time?"

00:07:14.667 --> 00:07:15.758
You will only say

00:07:15.783 --> 00:07:19.057
"I was here only and why i was searching for it all over the world?"

00:07:19.658 --> 00:07:23.403
This is actually happening.

00:07:23.428 --> 00:07:26.699
When we get such a state on account of Sahaj Yoga

00:07:26.724 --> 00:07:33.790
actually we get it so easily

00:07:33.815 --> 00:07:36.396
that we cannot understand how did we achieve this state?

00:07:38.217 --> 00:07:45.543
Or say, that in the modern age, as you suddenly reach Moon

00:07:46.829 --> 00:07:47.865
You may not even know

00:07:47.890 --> 00:07:49.683
if you could reach Moon in a moment.

00:07:49.708 --> 00:07:52.859
If such an arrangement could be made

00:07:52.884 --> 00:07:58.307
it is quite possible that you will feel

00:07:58.332 --> 00:08:03.498
where did we reach?

00:08:03.523 --> 00:08:04.731
How is it possible?

00:08:04.756 --> 00:08:08.111
How did we reach Moon in a moment?

00:08:08.136 --> 00:08:12.016
In the same way this incident

00:08:12.112 --> 00:08:15.917
takes place so easily

00:08:16.619 --> 00:08:19.014
this incident takes place so easily

00:08:19.039 --> 00:08:22.172
that it is quite natural for you to feel so.

00:08:22.197 --> 00:08:26.146
But, if something happens easily

00:08:26.436 --> 00:08:29.506
or with a great difficulty

00:08:29.531 --> 00:08:32.784
you remember one which takes place with a great difficulty.

00:08:32.809 --> 00:08:35.841
And one can understand that, which happens with difficulty.

00:08:35.866 --> 00:08:37.997
It is man's nature.

00:08:38.022 --> 00:08:41.134
And a man considers himself blessed in that

00:08:41.159 --> 00:08:44.007
which he gets by doing his duty.

00:08:44.032 --> 00:08:47.035
Even if his father gives him one lakh rupees

00:08:47.060 --> 00:08:49.195
he doesn't understand its importance.

00:08:49.220 --> 00:08:52.556
If he earns even two rupees by dint of his hard work

00:08:52.581 --> 00:08:53.582
he has great importance for it

00:08:53.607 --> 00:08:55.238
as he feels it is because of his own effort.

00:08:55.245 --> 00:08:57.554
It is an indication of his own ego.

00:08:57.579 --> 00:09:00.025
It is the nature of his Ego.

00:09:00.050 --> 00:09:03.488
But in Sahaj Yoga when there is no Ego

00:09:03.513 --> 00:09:06.512
there is no question of getting anything because of Ego.

00:09:06.769 --> 00:09:09.927
So ego being dissatisfied

00:09:09.952 --> 00:09:12.433
raises such doubts within

00:09:12.458 --> 00:09:15.155
that why it is so in Sahaj?

