00:13:09.988 --> 00:13:11.769
exactly you must think

00:13:11.794 --> 00:13:15.535
that every minute i have a new experience, it is a new thing.

00:13:15.560 --> 00:13:17.932
We are new people, everything is new.

00:13:17.957 --> 00:13:20.860
