00:17:35.156 --> 00:17:40.452
your attention can go towards anything as well as return back

00:17:40.477 --> 00:17:44.175
NOT CLEAR

00:17:44.200 --> 00:17:47.710
See our attention has gone towards some object.

00:17:47.734 --> 00:17:52.258
For example, your attention is on some saree.

00:17:52.283 --> 00:17:57.777
Your attention has gone towards saree but you can pull it back.

00:17:57.802 --> 00:18:03.337
As per your desire, you can minimize or maximize your attention

00:18:03.362 --> 00:18:05.902
and you can take it wherever you want.

00:18:05.927 --> 00:18:08.543
But you are fully involved in the center.

00:18:08.568 --> 00:18:09.793
For example, take the case of sea.

00:18:09.818 --> 00:18:13.944
the water from the sea overflows all its banks and returns back.

00:18:13.969 --> 00:18:16.988
but in the center, everything of the sea

00:18:17.013 --> 00:18:19.968
has its own abode (VASTAVYA)

00:18:19.993 --> 00:18:23.464
all that is VASTAVYA

00:18:23.489 --> 00:18:25.647
that which is going to happen, is inside.

00:18:25.672 --> 00:18:29.464
Its reaction is awareness.

00:18:29.489 --> 00:18:32.518
It goes to something and returns back.

00:18:32.543 --> 00:18:36.007
You learn detachment from this.

00:18:36.032 --> 00:18:39.217
From this only we tell you to get detatched.

00:18:39.242 --> 00:18:41.873
For example that car came here.

00:18:41.898 --> 00:18:45.190
It is a minor issue. it is giving out some smell

00:18:45.215 --> 00:18:47.777
First of all, it gave out foul smell, o.k!

00:18:47.802 --> 00:18:51.059
If you pay attention to the foul smell, we will feel it.

00:18:51.084 --> 00:18:52.373
You divert your attention, you will not feel foul smell.

00:18:55.695 --> 00:18:58.959
You are getting the power of detachment within you.

00:18:58.984 --> 00:19:02.249
By and by you practice over your attention

00:19:02.274 --> 00:19:09.975
Man endowed with all religious knowledge is sitting in the center.

00:19:10.000 --> 00:19:11.825
He is paying attention to everything.

00:19:11.850 --> 00:19:14.471
What is this, what is this, what is this?

00:19:14.496 --> 00:19:17.348
This is also,This is also, people say all this is mine.

00:19:17.373 --> 00:19:19.146
Pay your attention to that

00:19:19.171 --> 00:19:21.697
and the moment you pay attention to that

00:19:21.722 --> 00:19:24.324
you know very well that I can take it back as well from there.

00:19:24.349 --> 00:19:27.094
Your attention cannot get involved in any such thing

00:19:30.399 --> 00:19:36.065
and whatever love you will attatch to it or do anything

00:19:36.090 --> 00:19:39.086
that will only hit it with a stone and come back

00:19:39.111 --> 00:19:42.877
but will not get attatched to it.

00:19:42.902 --> 00:19:44.379
Try to understand it.

00:19:44.404 --> 00:19:47.097
Eirlier when you would pay your attention to a thing

00:19:47.122 --> 00:19:48.302
with the help of your thoughts.

00:19:48.327 --> 00:19:50.742
For example, if anything moves from here

00:19:50.767 --> 00:19:54.165
that will go on moving as a whole and its range will be maintained.

00:19:54.190 --> 00:19:55.896
NOT CLEAR

00:19:55.921 --> 00:19:57.868
Now the one that will get released from here

00:19:57.893 --> 00:20:00.076
will take a round turn and then will come towards you.

00:20:00.101 --> 00:20:01.445
There is nothing in the center.

00:20:01.473 --> 00:20:01.935
It is all vacant.

00:20:06.220 --> 00:20:07.901
Nowhere it will put a hurdle.

00:20:07.926 --> 00:20:11.147
In this way attatchment attracts everything.

00:20:11.172 --> 00:20:13.945
One gets rid of  body, mind and intellect definitely

00:20:13.970 --> 00:20:17.874
but of other misidentifications within us too.

00:20:17.899 --> 00:20:19.950
We are human beings first

00:20:19.975 --> 00:20:25.067
and finally this truth, and this truth also detaches from us

00:20:25.092 --> 00:20:29.826
because we do not give up our attatchment

00:20:29.851 --> 00:20:32.597
and the method to give up attatchment during meditation is

00:20:32.622 --> 00:20:36.304
that you increase your attention and enjoy it.

00:20:36.329 --> 00:20:37.106
Now it has increased.

00:20:37.131 --> 00:20:39.996
Go there and you get it back.

00:20:40.021 --> 00:20:44.543
This special power you got after your realization

00:20:44.568 --> 00:20:47.695
I have already told you a lot of things

00:20:47.720 --> 00:20:51.912
Apart from this, keep in mind that

00:20:51.937 --> 00:20:55.574
in deeper meditation you have to do

00:20:55.599 --> 00:20:59.747
expansion and stretching of your attention.

00:20:59.772 --> 00:21:03.015
When you will be stretching and expanding your attention

00:21:03.040 --> 00:21:06.706
you will be surprised that your depth has increased.

00:21:06.731 --> 00:21:12.159
Just imagine that if you spread a lot of wheat here

00:21:12.184 --> 00:21:16.111
the person who has spread a lot of wheat, his stretch will be more

00:21:16.135 --> 00:21:19.252
then when you collected wheat and piled up

00:21:19.410 --> 00:21:21.491
has its height increased or not?

00:21:21.516 --> 00:21:26.748
In the same way when you have wrapped up your attention

00:21:26.773 --> 00:21:29.115
your inner depth will increase

00:21:29.139 --> 00:21:31.514
and what knowledge you got

00:21:31.553 --> 00:21:33.020
it excited my laughter to know

00:21:33.045 --> 00:21:35.511
was i wrapped in this?

00:21:35.536 --> 00:21:37.861
Was it worth getting wrapped up into?

00:21:37.886 --> 00:21:40.581
Means it will appear that it was not so important.

00:21:40.606 --> 00:21:43.767
These are not at all very important issues of the world.

00:21:43.792 --> 00:21:47.041
In our country there is a boy who had got realization.

00:21:47.066 --> 00:21:48.783
He went for an interview.

00:21:48.808 --> 00:21:49.840
When he returned back

00:21:49.865 --> 00:21:51.124
I asked him have you got through the interview or not?

00:21:51.149 --> 00:21:53.449
He said," I don't feel anything, if i have got through or not.

00:21:53.474 --> 00:21:55.188
In case i get through, it is good, if not, no problem."

00:21:55.213 --> 00:21:57.430
Finally he was selected.

00:21:57.455 --> 00:22:00.288
Board people told ME

00:22:00.313 --> 00:22:03.806
He was a special boy. He came and was not afraid at all.

00:22:03.831 --> 00:22:08.712
He gave straight forward answers and left, he was not afraid at all.

00:22:09.629 --> 00:22:11.397
How is he so?

00:22:11.422 --> 00:22:13.754
I said,"I had told you that he is realized.

00:22:13.779 --> 00:22:17.201
You examine him specially to find out, what is so special about him?"

00:22:17.226 --> 00:22:19.393
He said,  "We observed that

00:22:19.418 --> 00:22:22.163
he came, he answered straight forwardly the questions he was put to."

00:22:22.188 --> 00:22:24.163
He didn't have any trickery, nor anything.

00:22:24.188 --> 00:22:27.074
He was very straight forward, talked straight forwardly

00:22:27.099 --> 00:22:28.999
and then he kept standing

00:22:29.024 --> 00:22:32.707
and said, if he gets through, well and good, otherwise no problem.

00:22:32.732 --> 00:22:35.610
Neither he disrespected us in any way

00:22:35.635 --> 00:22:39.923
nor he wagged his tail behind us.

00:22:42.155 --> 00:22:43.395
Attention is also like that.

00:22:43.420 --> 00:22:45.879
When there is deformation in attention

00:22:45.904 --> 00:22:49.455
man gets divinity when he gets realized.

00:22:49.480 --> 00:22:52.669
When his attention is messy everywhere

00:22:52.694 --> 00:22:54.701
his attention distorts.

00:22:54.726 --> 00:22:57.345
Just try to understand

00:22:57.370 --> 00:23:02.197
you must have seen, just as tendrils come out of many trees

00:23:02.222 --> 00:23:06.624
specially the creepers

00:23:06.649 --> 00:23:11.233
(tendrils) come out and catch hold of this, catch hold of that

00:23:11.258 --> 00:23:15.027
then slowly and slowly it climbs up.

00:23:15.066 --> 00:23:18.219
In the same way, a man who is not realized

00:23:18.244 --> 00:23:22.037
he also catches sometimes this, sometimes that and sometimes that.

00:23:22.062 --> 00:23:24.247
In this way he some how stands up.

00:23:24.272 --> 00:23:27.054
Sometimes he thinks that he doesn't have a position.

00:23:27.079 --> 00:23:28.734
How will i survive on the earth?

00:23:28.759 --> 00:23:30.076
Oh! i don't have money.

00:23:30.101 --> 00:23:31.648
How will i survive in the world?

00:23:31.673 --> 00:23:33.047
Oh! i don't have this

00:23:33.072 --> 00:23:34.564
How will i survive in the world?

00:23:34.589 --> 00:23:37.256
But the tree that stands on its trunk

00:23:37.281 --> 00:23:39.791
looks quite independant.

00:23:39.816 --> 00:23:42.426
But the same thing is happening to you too.

00:23:43.280 --> 00:23:45.384
You are no doubt standing on your trunk

00:23:45.408 --> 00:23:48.923
but because of fear you take out tentricles from inside

00:23:48.948 --> 00:23:54.264
catch hold of this, catch hold of that and so on.

00:23:54.289 --> 00:23:56.560
For example, you know where you are standing

00:23:56.585 --> 00:23:58.159
this is the second thing which you should know.

00:23:58.458 --> 00:24:01.913
First thing is that you should not control your attention.

00:24:01.938 --> 00:24:03.576
It should not be controlled.

00:24:03.601 --> 00:24:05.528
Attention will not be tangled at all.

00:24:05.553 --> 00:24:08.434
You try, it will never tangle

00:24:08.459 --> 00:24:10.772
You try in deep meditation.

00:24:10.796 --> 00:24:12.590
You may have any major question.

00:24:12.615 --> 00:24:14.935
You look at it.

00:24:14.960 --> 00:24:17.626
Just on looking at it, you will be surprised that

00:24:17.651 --> 00:24:19.760
your attention goes there and returns back.

00:24:19.785 --> 00:24:21.332
Attention cannot entangle anywhere.

00:24:21.357 --> 00:24:22.988
Then you just think.

00:24:23.013 --> 00:24:25.792
For example, a great sad incident has taken place.

00:24:25.817 --> 00:24:28.073
You think that here a very sad incident has taken place

00:24:28.098 --> 00:24:30.371
but the world is going on as usual.

00:24:30.396 --> 00:24:35.297
Sorrow and happiness is our mind's creation.

00:24:35.900 --> 00:24:42.139
What is it, that makes us very sad or very happy.

00:24:42.164 --> 00:24:49.877
Or what is it that we hate someone or love another.

00:24:49.901 --> 00:24:52.626
There is no such thing which should lead to it.

00:24:52.651 --> 00:24:59.493
By and by your attention will circulate with a great speed.

00:24:59.518 --> 00:25:03.807
and then when attention gets fixed, gets absolutely fixed

00:25:03.832 --> 00:25:06.292
whosoever we look at

00:25:07.022 --> 00:25:10.661
you have also seen that by touching somebody, our hands burn

00:25:10.686 --> 00:25:13.636
by working on somebody, we catch.

00:25:13.661 --> 00:25:16.183
In the beginning it will happen so.

00:25:16.935 --> 00:25:18.105
Be away from him.

00:25:18.130 --> 00:25:20.553
As far as possible, do not put your hand in the furnace.

00:25:20.578 --> 00:25:22.787
When a girl learns to cook food

00:25:22.812 --> 00:25:27.485
first of all she cooks on a small oven by wrapping a small cloth.

00:25:27.510 --> 00:25:32.316
when she learns to manage a little, then she starts cooking on a big oven.

00:25:32.341 --> 00:25:34.946
In that too, she first holds tongs

00:25:34.971 --> 00:25:36.776
then handles a TAWA (iron plate to bake bread)

00:25:36.801 --> 00:25:37.819
and bakes a ROTI (Indian bread) on it.

00:25:37.844 --> 00:25:42.093
When she becomes an expert, she makes ROTI with hands.

00:25:42.118 --> 00:25:45.107
She can put her hand in the oven as well.

00:25:45.132 --> 00:25:49.262
In the same way, in the beginning what we call an evil

00:25:49.287 --> 00:25:52.726
what we call bad even that will  (NOT CLEAR).

00:25:52.751 --> 00:25:57.695
And what we call evil, will by itself go out wherever you stand.

00:25:57.720 --> 00:26:00.423
It won't effect you.

00:26:00.448 --> 00:26:02.328
When you will be in such a state

00:26:02.353 --> 00:26:04.015
what is the need of Mother's protection?

00:26:04.040 --> 00:26:05.964
You will grow yourself.

00:26:08.802 --> 00:26:11.840
Then you won't catch from anyone , nothing

00:26:11.865 --> 00:26:13.098
whosoever may be at whatever place

00:26:13.123 --> 00:26:14.583
you go and find out nothing.

00:26:14.608 --> 00:26:17.486
He who reaches there, is running away from there.

00:26:17.511 --> 00:26:19.057
They themselves are not going to stay there.

00:26:19.082 --> 00:26:21.459
When you achieve that ability

00:26:21.484 --> 00:26:24.844
that day, these questions are appropriate for all times to come.

00:26:26.360 --> 00:26:28.672
But as I had told you that

00:26:28.697 --> 00:26:29.789
there are only two methods of it.

00:26:29.814 --> 00:26:33.669
One is inside meditation, and the other is external (NOT CLEAR).

00:26:33.694 --> 00:26:36.929
Now something is going out of your hand.

00:26:36.954 --> 00:26:41.532
First of all they speak of good KARMAS

00:26:41.557 --> 00:26:44.034
do good, do bad

00:26:44.059 --> 00:26:49.310
good or bad is man's thought process.

00:26:49.335 --> 00:26:51.250
When KARMA becomes AKARMA

00:26:51.275 --> 00:26:53.925
means if there is no such feeling that we are doing KARMA

00:26:53.950 --> 00:26:55.004
for example, there is light of the Sun

00:26:55.029 --> 00:26:56.236
what Karma is HE doing?

00:26:56.261 --> 00:26:58.660
HE is in AKARMA, but He is doing KARMA.

00:27:01.428 --> 00:27:03.816
When there is complete AKARMA

00:27:03.841 --> 00:27:06.647
that something is flowing in hand and happening

00:27:06.672 --> 00:27:10.212
whatever KARMAS of the past have accumulated inside us

00:27:10.237 --> 00:27:12.361
it is said that you will have to bear the reward of your actions.

00:27:12.386 --> 00:27:13.601
Many sick people come here

00:27:13.626 --> 00:27:15.245
saying, Mataji these are the rewards of our KARMAS.

00:27:15.270 --> 00:27:16.172
Will you take out these?

00:27:16.196 --> 00:27:19.004
I say, yes I will take these. Don't worry.

00:27:19.029 --> 00:27:21.658
When we come to Ganga ji, these should get washed off.

00:27:21.684 --> 00:27:24.882
If on account of your Karmas your hands and feet are paining

00:27:24.907 --> 00:27:26.760
if you have fallen sick and then got some trouble

00:27:26.785 --> 00:27:30.123
it hardly matters, I can take that.

00:27:30.148 --> 00:27:33.571
But your Karmas have travelled from your body to your mind.

00:27:35.719 --> 00:27:38.178
How will karmas from your mind dissolve?

00:27:40.932 --> 00:27:42.332
These are standing outside.

00:27:42.357 --> 00:27:44.405
Because of Mataji, your health has improved

00:27:44.430 --> 00:27:46.874
but these karmas are settled in the mind.

00:27:46.899 --> 00:27:48.082
You have got your realization

00:27:48.107 --> 00:27:50.142
still how will this filth come out?

00:27:50.167 --> 00:27:52.670
So, when you will be doing this karma

00:27:52.695 --> 00:27:54.735
it will all flow down into akarma.

00:27:56.705 --> 00:27:59.171
And as much you will do in this lifetime

00:27:59.196 --> 00:28:07.890
your karma will come to an end.

00:28:07.915 --> 00:28:10.739
By and by, when you will go on doing Karmas

00:28:10.764 --> 00:28:12.054
these will go on quiting like this.

00:28:12.078 --> 00:28:14.969
After all the cleanliness of your inside being is over

00:28:14.994 --> 00:28:17.333
the same feeling of pity inside your being

00:28:17.359 --> 00:28:21.465
liking and disliking nothing remains there.

00:28:21.490 --> 00:28:25.763
You are sitting, you may or may not get food to eat.

00:28:25.788 --> 00:28:26.946
Whatever work you are doing

00:28:26.971 --> 00:28:30.057
if you are an executive, or any entity of the world

00:28:30.082 --> 00:28:33.576
you are doing that work only which is of God.

00:28:33.601 --> 00:28:36.006
You are not doing any of your personal work.

00:28:36.031 --> 00:28:39.957
Its work is being done by your hands and you are unaware of it.

00:28:40.005 --> 00:28:42.964
For example, Sun is giving its own light.

00:28:42.989 --> 00:28:46.747
Moon is enjoying Sun's light within itself.

00:28:46.772 --> 00:28:52.572
The sea is ascending, descending and sending out clouds.

00:28:52.597 --> 00:28:54.157
Their karmas are active

00:28:54.182 --> 00:28:59.347
but nobody thinks that he is doing anything.

00:28:59.372 --> 00:29:01.723
There are trees, from trees fruits come out

00:29:01.748 --> 00:29:04.259
seeds come out of trees and then trees come out of these.

00:29:04.284 --> 00:29:06.198
How much occupied they are in such a major work?

00:29:06.223 --> 00:29:08.979
But none of them that they are doing anything.

00:29:09.004 --> 00:29:10.833
Everything goes on smoothly.

00:29:10.858 --> 00:29:13.163
Only man has a question.

00:29:13.188 --> 00:29:15.028
All of them are in harmony.

00:29:15.053 --> 00:29:16.538
We have questions

00:29:16.563 --> 00:29:21.501
because God Himself has given specially this boon of ego to mankind

00:29:21.526 --> 00:29:23.098
so that we know Him.

00:29:24.019 --> 00:29:27.245
But we have seen that ego doesn't die by striking it

00:29:27.270 --> 00:29:30.108
So it should depart by itself.

00:29:30.133 --> 00:29:31.891
That is the method of Sahajyoga.

00:29:31.916 --> 00:29:34.068
It exits by itself, that too you have seen.

00:29:34.093 --> 00:29:35.601
But what should be done?

00:29:35.626 --> 00:29:38.473
You should do yourself as much karma as you can

00:29:38.791 --> 00:29:42.350
and another is to go into deep meditation.

00:29:42.375 --> 00:29:47.700
unless you reach that stage where there is nothing called good or bad.

00:29:47.725 --> 00:29:49.546
You have seen ME, I go anywhere

00:29:49.571 --> 00:29:52.461
neither any negativity catches ME, nor any Bhoot

00:29:52.486 --> 00:29:54.709
neither MY finger, nor MY hand.

00:29:54.734 --> 00:29:56.555
Everytime there should be such flow only.

00:29:56.580 --> 00:29:59.246
Iif you feel any heat from MY head

00:29:59.271 --> 00:30:02.669
that means it is some negativity within you only

00:30:02.694 --> 00:30:06.070
it is an example in front of you.

00:30:06.095 --> 00:30:09.888
I am also like you only, but an example in front of you.

00:30:09.913 --> 00:30:12.235
In the same way, when you will be Shivji

00:30:12.260 --> 00:30:15.447
neither there will be any devil nor a bad being.

00:30:15.472 --> 00:30:18.293
Whosoever comes in front of you, should get mingled in your love

00:30:18.318 --> 00:30:20.058
and if he doesn't get, he will run away.

00:30:20.083 --> 00:30:21.630
When there will be such a situation

00:30:21.655 --> 00:30:25.868
that day you won't need this protection.

00:30:25.893 --> 00:30:29.428
You only have found out many ways to protect yourself.

00:30:29.453 --> 00:30:31.767
Whatever the methods are there

00:30:31.792 --> 00:30:35.860
if you want they can tell you what they use.

00:30:35.885 --> 00:30:38.551
Whatever they use or you can ask them

00:30:38.575 --> 00:30:44.221
for example, (MY) photograph, foot soak, giving bandhan to yourself

00:30:44.246 --> 00:30:48.879
to take different names and many other things

00:30:48.904 --> 00:30:51.640
for that if you want, you can talk to them

00:30:51.665 --> 00:30:52.963
and they will tell you everything.

00:30:52.988 --> 00:30:56.412
But a realized person during meditation

00:30:56.437 --> 00:30:59.131
first after sitting must introspect

00:30:59.156 --> 00:31:01.769
if there is any catch from what he is receiving.

00:31:01.794 --> 00:31:03.641
If we are getting vibrations

00:31:03.666 --> 00:31:05.356
If there are no vibrations, he should get rid of catches.

00:31:05.381 --> 00:31:07.498
How should he take it out and what should he do

00:31:07.523 --> 00:31:09.201
Sharad also can tell you, these people can tell you

00:31:09.226 --> 00:31:11.436
how the blocked vibrations have to be cleared.

00:31:11.461 --> 00:31:14.424
If there is burning sensation in hands, how should it be taken out.

00:31:14.449 --> 00:31:16.295
Take it out that time

00:31:16.320 --> 00:31:17.162
by taking the name (of the Diety of that chakra)

00:31:17.187 --> 00:31:18.682
it will come out.

00:31:18.707 --> 00:31:21.741
it will come out in such a way that you will feel it was never there.

00:31:21.766 --> 00:31:24.926
You catch from the atmosphere, from plants, from everywhere

00:31:24.951 --> 00:31:28.702
Your situation is just like a small girl who learns cooking food.

00:31:30.166 --> 00:31:33.228
When you will be expert in this field

00:31:33.253 --> 00:31:35.209
then only you will be real yogi.

00:31:35.234 --> 00:31:37.384
Because there will be complete efficiency

